<p>This update reshapes how Google ranks content by emphasizing expertise, technical performance, and AI signals. The changes represent a fundamental shift in how search engines evaluate and rank websites.</p>

<p>Google's AI-driven ranking signals have become much stronger, meaning:</p>

<ul>
